    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1366px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Stefano Chermaz</h1>
      
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl mb-6">
          IT consultant specialized in Microsoft 365, artificial intelligence, and business compliance.
        </p>
        
